&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That &lt;a href=&quot;https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cleartext&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;cleartext&lt;/a&gt; security information has been passing through my tunnels ever since I started working on that server. It was simply time to move one step up in the world of authentication - it was time to use some &lt;em&gt;cryptography&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
      
